  "text": "Plastics are estimated to last hundreds to thousands of years in marine systems [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , and are dispersed through the action of waves, currents and fouling activity [CITATION_3] . The longevity and wide distribution of plastic facilitates interaction with a range of marine organisms.",
